Submission
----------
Deadline for submission : Sept 29 th, 2000

All submissions must be either written and/or presented in French;
They cannot have more than 15 pages; the LaTex style is mandatory and
can be found on the web site of the conference :
         http://pauillac.inria.fr/jfla/2001/jfla2001.sty

It is better to send a postscript file which can be directly printed under 
Unix; INRIA will edit the proceedings; the submissions must be sent
to the president of the program committee, with "jfla2001" in the 
mail subject, at the following address :   casteran@labri.u-bordeaux.fr


